# Example Data Licenses

## mumbai_chip.tif

**Source:** SpaceNet 5 Roads Dataset (AOI 8 - Mumbai)
**Original file:** SN5_roads_train_AOI_8_Mumbai_PS-RGB_chip0.tif
**License:** [CC BY-SA 4.0](https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0/)

WorldView-3 satellite imagery pan-sharpened to 0.3m resolution.

**Attribution:** The SpaceNet Dataset by SpaceNet Partners is licensed under a
Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 4.0 International License.

**Download:** `aws s3 cp s3://spacenet-dataset/spacenet/SN5_roads/train/AOI_8_Mumbai/PS-RGB/SN5_roads_train_AOI_8_Mumbai_PS-RGB_chip0.tif . --no-sign-request`
